{"tid":177483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"轟京干預特首選舉美國會：或撤港特權","createTime":"2017-03-29T01:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-29T02:15:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2889fffd1bfce1b55f5f11aee5a1b98784b7e3fc","tid":177483,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:42:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19973535&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170329\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19973535%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170329&d=u6uLjzzFZj4TH%2F5rj7Ekc54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=848b1a37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D19973535%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170329&h=f9ffaa38\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=19973535&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170329</a><br />\n<br />\n轟京干預特首選舉<br />\n美國會：或撤港特權<br />\n<br />\n頭條&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國國會及行政當局中國委員會（Congressional-Executive Commission on China）就香港特首選舉發表聲明，指出中央介入選舉，透過向選委施壓，要求他們票投林鄭月娥，違反《基本法》及高度自治，警告香港若淪為大陸城市，或會喪失特權。<br />\n<br />\n美國國會及行政當局中國委員會負責監察中國的法治發展和人權。身兼委員會主席的美國國會眾議員魯比奧（Marco Rubio）以及聯合主席史密夫（Christopher Smith）就林鄭月娥日前當選新一屆特首發表聲明，批評中央介入香港特首選舉。<br />\n<br />\n恐港淪為大陸城市<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧於聲明指，今次特首選舉仍然未能滿足香港人爭取普選、政府須具代表性的要求，「北京在今次選舉中明顯的干預，是削弱香港多年抱持自治的另一例子。在選舉結果公佈後的數個小時，幾位雨傘運動的領袖因為參與爭取民主運動，而面對新一輪的檢控」。聲明指，林鄭有必要採取積極行動重啟政改，以符合港人對民主的盼望。<br />\n<br />\n史密夫則於聲明指出，林鄭一如多位前任特首是北京喜歡的候選人，但這會令到香港自治、法治不斷被侵蝕的問題難以處理（just like her predecessors, and this will make it exceedingly difficult to deal with the constant erosions of Hong Kong's autonomy and rule of law），又認為如果香港在新特首領導之下，淪為中國大陸另一個城市，「我們就要重新評估香港是否仍依照美國法律享有特權」。<br />\n<br />\n委員會認為，本港的特首選舉原已極多掣肘，但北京政府官員更透過向選委會委員施壓，要求他們票投林鄭，而人大委員長張德江亦據報維護中央過問特首選舉的權力。委員會指這些舉動均違反《基本法》第22條、第45條、以及香港在國際條約下的義務。<br />\n<br />\n■記者姚國雄"},{"pid":"72e2853e070609cbded9e596c29ee300aaa515b7","tid":177483,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:45:49.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n<br />\n全部人一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40df0e001a97ed17d95ea3b514c18c84625f48b","tid":177483,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:47:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0b9e5676c6d23597f0cc08ebc4a0c5df389c41d","tid":177483,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:48:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<br />\n<br />\n全部人一齊攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撤唔撤對呢到好多人黎講都冇影響 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5bf4582043c24058c80a07a599f04985d7b406f","tid":177483,"uid":44547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"講下而家香港有咩特權咁巴閉先啦"},{"pid":"0857b84e9dd785f032f64ad2888293f7825ed31b","tid":177483,"uid":92118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:49:45.000Z","msg":"我地住緊既係，深圳市香港縣"},{"pid":"b05b81ba3cfacd73d127d0ad43bbcd70905603f8","tid":177483,"uid":37986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:51:34.000Z","msg":"京干預唔使你教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d91d68b3610e5eafa6f9994f654cece95267a4d","tid":177483,"uid":34760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T01:53:09.000Z","msg":"3個月就講一次 幾時肯cut?仲難cut過有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e3416c4475d17385d0f842577de6f57a4750e9f","tid":177483,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-29T02:15:15.000Z","msg":"焦土撚happy<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/superman.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"